WEBVTT

00:00.885 --> 00:02.381
Previously on "The Originals"...

00:02.382 --> 00:04.784
This town was my home.
I want it back.

00:04.785 --> 00:07.025
All of your scheming,
the enemies that you have made

00:07.026 --> 00:09.243
every single day
of your miserable life,

00:09.244 --> 00:11.528
what results did you expect,

00:11.529 --> 00:14.032
that your child would be born
into a happy life?

00:14.033 --> 00:16.426
This was our family's hope.

00:16.427 --> 00:18.120
We need to regain
control of the city.

00:18.121 --> 00:20.138
You want allies, right?

00:20.139 --> 00:23.007
This is ground zero
for a new vampire community.

00:23.008 --> 00:24.629
You may think that
you're better than us.

00:24.630 --> 00:25.897
We're all you got.

00:26.703 --> 00:29.280
We made a deal.
He'll pledge his loyalty to Cassie,

00:29.281 --> 00:31.582
report back, and tell me
everything that he learns.

00:31.583 --> 00:33.036
Her name is Gia.

00:33.037 --> 00:34.449
She's the first one
that I turned.

00:34.450 --> 00:36.321
She's gonna need a mentor.

00:36.322 --> 00:38.200
We should've known our
mother would not be bound

00:38.201 --> 00:41.827
- by anything as obvious as death.
- Where is she?

00:41.828 --> 00:46.496
Finn, Kol, we have
a family reunion to plan.

